        <updateDate>2012-04-25T21:11:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Postal Executive Accountability Act - Prohibits bonuses or other rewards to the Postmaster General or any other officer of the U.S. Postal Service (USPS) in a senior executive position in any year in which any postal retail facility or mail processing facility is closed.</p> <p>Repeals exceptions to the limit on total compensation for USPS officers and employees.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
